-117 on to (North RD,", "Sudbury/Waltham Street Maynard.) That can be really dangerous. It will also eliminate the chance of", "getting on the wrong section(s) of Old Mill Rd.", "From: First Parish Church, Framingham:", "Go North on Edgell Rd, turn RIGHT on Boston Post Road (RT-20) and a quick LEFT to Union Ave.", "Follow to end and turn LEFT on Concord Rd, Toward Sudbury Center. In Sudbury Center continue", "STRAIGHT on CONCORD RD. to PANTRY RD. (Where Concord RD turns right, you keep going STRAIGHT.)", "At the traffic lights at Rt-117, Turn LEFT. Turn RIGHT at St. Johns Lutheran Church (NORTH RD.", "(Sudbury). This will become Waltham Street when you enter MAYNARD. Old Mill Rd will be a half mile", "up the street on the RIGHT. Look for the orange and black Maynard Rod and Gun Club Sign on the", "telephone pole at the corner of Old Mill Rd and Waltham Street. (Its easier to see it at night when it lit.)", "Old Mill Rd is a very narrow street, play nice with on coming traffic. Follow the street to the RIGHT into", "the Rod and Gun Parking Lot. The Pavilion is the large building down the hill.", "Maynard", "1.3mi", "ke", "Sudbury", "Hudson", "Framingham", "May 21, 2021 Directions: Maynard Rod & Gun Club - 1 - Rev:"], "bbox": [[0.336405, 0.093649, 0.32675400000000004, 0.013889], [0.448497, 0.110581, 0.10274500000000003, 0.013889], [0.423007, 0.127487, 0.15410499999999994, 0.013889], [0.117688, 0.161578, 0.6696369999999999, 0.013889], [0.117688, 0.178497, 0.739017, 0.013889], [0.117688, 0.195455, 0.336198, 0.013889], [0.121609, 0.246212, 0.28886999999999996, 0.013889], [0.176503, 0.263131, 0.692261, 0.013889], [0.117688, 0.280303, 0.714199, 0.013889], [0.117688, 0.297222, 0.752762, 0.013889], [0.117688, 0.314141, 0.68791, 0.013889], [0.117688, 0.331086, 0.7512709999999999, 0.013889], [0.117688, 0.348005, 0.712375, 0.013889], [0.117688, 0.364924, 0.758926, 0.013889], [0.117688, 0.381843, 0.757379, 0.013889], [0.117688, 0.398775, 0.56083, 0.013889], [0.090564, 0.498295, 